    <h2> FAQ </h2>

    <h3>Why Dial4Jobz?</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>In Dial4jobz you can get candidates for all categories. </li>
        <li>Dial4jobz does not limit candidates to Internet users.</li>
	    <li>Candidates can register their Resume over phone by calling 044 - 44455566</li>
	    <li>Because of this Dial4jobz has taken out financial, cultural, educational and Linguistic barriers.</li>
	    <li>You have options of getting Resumes by SMS.</li>
	    <li>As soon as a jobseeker submits his/her resume (through internet or over phone)& if the resume suits your vacancy you can prefer to get that Resume by SMS or/& email immediately.</li>
	    <li>Your recruitment cost per candidate can be & will be most of the time lesser than Rs.500/-</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Do I have to pay for every resume I view in Dial4jobz?</h3>
        <ul>
         <li> No you don’t have to pay for viewing the resume.</li>
	     <li>You are paying only for the shortlisted candidates or to whom you want to communicate.</li>
	     <li>You pay only for viewing the contact details of the candidate.</li>
        </ul>

    <h3>How many resumes I can view?</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>You can view any number of resumes from any category.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How Accurate will be the Data of the candidate?</h3>

    <ul>
        <li>Job seekers when they register their data either by phone or through internet their mobile number is verified & a verification mail is sent his/her mail id to verify the email id.</li>
        <li>Once the verification is complete the data will show as “verified” otherwise it will show as” pending verification” </li>
        <li>If background check is done for the  candidate it will reflect in his/her resume as verified </li>
        <li>All the information/data is as communicated or furnished by the candidate over phone or through internet.</li>
        <li>It shall be the sole responsibility of the Employer before appointing them to check, authenticate and verify the information/ response received. Dial4jobz is not responsible for false information given by the candidate.</li>
        <li>For your benefit you can do verification or background check through Dial4Jobz.</li>
    </ul>

